O Lord!
तव पादतलं
soles (lower part) of Thy feet
वदन्ति
is said to be
पाद-ऊर्ध्व-देशम्-अपि
the upper surface of (Thy) feet
देव
O Effulgent One!
रसातलं
(is) Rasaatala
ते गुल्फद्वयं खलु
Thy two ankles, indeed
महातलम्-
