s6
00:00:53.833 --> 00:01:34.666 align:start
जङ्घे तलातलम्-
(Thy) shins Talaatal
अथ: सुतलं च जानू
then, Sutala (are Thy) knees
किञ्च-उरु-भाग-युगलं
moreover, the two thighs (are)
वितल-अतले द्वे
the two (worlds) Vitala and Atala
क्षोणीतलं जघनम्-
the earth is (Thy) hip
अम्बरम्-अङ्ग नाभि: -
sky is O Lord! the navel
